---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="Hotels & apartments — Gandía, summer 2026"
	description="We search hotels, apartments and casas rurales for you for summer 2026 — by your budget and your preferred area. Tell us your range and where you'd love to wake up; we shortlist, you pick, we book."
	otherLangHref="/es/hoteles/"
	otherLangLabel="Español"
>
	<p class="eyebrow">Hotels & apartments</p>
	<h1>Where you'll <span class="accent">stay</span></h1>
	<p class="tagline">
		Tell us your budget and where you'd love to wake up — we search,
		shortlist and book.
	</p>

	<p>
		Hotels, apartments, <em>casas rurales</em>, villas, family resorts —
		the right place depends on two things: <strong>where you want your
		days to start</strong>, and <strong>what you want to spend</strong>.
		Tell us those two, and <strong>we'll search for you</strong> —
		comparing what's available for your dates, talking to the houses we
		know, putting together two or three options that fit. You pick; we
		book the room and handle the rest.
	</p>

	<h2 class="zone-heading">Where we look</h2>

	<div class="zone-grid">
		<article class="zone-card">
			<h3>Playa de Gandía</h3>
			<p>Beachfront apartments and family resorts on the long sandy bay — soft sand, palm-lined promenade, the easiest base for a beach week.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="zone-card">
			<h3>Gandía old town</h3>
			<p>Small boutique hotels around the Palau Ducal — walkable, full of cafés, evening life that runs late.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="zone-card">
			<h3>The calas — Xàbia, Moraira, Calpe, Altea</h3>
			<p>Villas and apartments tucked above the coves — cliffs, pines, turquoise water at the bottom of the road.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="zone-card">
			<h3>Inland Marina Alta</h3>
			<p><em>Casas rurales</em> and small mountain inns in Bocairent, the Vall de Gallinera, Tàrbena — cooler nights, real stars, hiking from the doorstep.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="zone-card">
			<h3>Benidorm</h3>
			<p>Big family-friendly resorts on Playa de Levante — half an hour down the coast, kids' pools, all-inclusive options.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="zone-card">
			<h3>Valencia city</h3>
			<p>Boutique stays in the old quarter — an hour by train from Gandía, ideal for a city night before or after the coast.</p>
		</article>
	</div>

	<p>
		<strong>We work to any budget.</strong> From comfortable family
		apartments and resorts at the lower end, through boutique hotels and
		characterful villas in the middle, to high-end seafront suites and
		full villa rentals at the upper end. Tell us your range; we come back
		with two or three options that fit, with honest notes on each.
	</p>

	<p class="signoff">
		You don't book through a search engine, you book through someone who
		knows the street.
	</p>

	<p class="cta-top">
		<a class="cta" href="/#contact">Tell us what you'd like →</a>
	</p>

	<style>
		.zone-heading {
			font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
			font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 1.85rem);
			font-weight: 700;
			letter-spacing: -0.01em;
			margin: 2.8rem 0 1.4rem;
			color: var(--accent);
			text-align: center;
		}
		.zone-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			gap: 1.1rem;
			margin: 0 0 2.6rem;
		}
		.zone-card {
			background: var(--paper);
			border: 1px solid var(--rule);
			border-radius: 10px;
			padding: 1.4rem 1.4rem 1.2rem;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(31, 27, 22, 0.06);
			transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
		}
		.zone-card:hover {
			transform: translateY(-3px);
			box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(31, 27, 22, 0.12);
		}
		.zone-card h3 {
			font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
			font-size: 1.12rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.01em;
			color: var(--ink);
		}
		.zone-card p {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--muted);
			margin: 0;
			line-height: 1.55;
		}
		@media (max-width: 640px) {
			.zone-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
